<item>
            <title>[LU-8203] sanity-hsm test_60 failed as we do not wait for copytool operation to complete</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8203</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The copytool is trying to archive a 40mb file with the bandwidth limitation of 1mbps and the script kills the copytool before it has finished archiving. This causes the status of the copytool to remain started. As a result, the copytool fails to archive the next time it is turned on to archive the same file.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
